title: Build.a.Lot-SKIDROW
description:
Release Notes:

Make yourself a real estate mogul and dominate the housing
market. In Build-a-lot, you can construct, upgrade and sell
houses for big-time profits. Flip houses for instant cash or
keep them as rental properties and sit back and collect the
rent. If you've ever wanted to try your hand at real estate,
this is your chance to become a powerful land baron.

Send the housing market through the roof in this exciting
property-building game. Two clever gameplay modes, Career and
Casual, give you a variety of ways for you to display your
real estate talents. Travel to various neighborhoods and
improve the right areas. Erect special buildings, including
museums, mansions and castles. Manage your houses and build
your empire to incredible levels of success.

Earn huge profits by successful managing the building and
selling of houses

Construct, upgrade and flip houses to become a real estate
